name: Condemned
description:
!!!UNSTABLE ALPHA PACK!!!

There is no code for this pack. It is currently set to private as it is still being built and balanced. I am looking for testers. If you would like to test it, please tweet me @TigerzFangz.

##Check the change logs BEFORE updating!##

To do this, go to the "Packs" tab and find this mod pack. Click on the "Website" button below the description and scroll to the bottom of the page. Then select the version number that you want to see the change log for.

This pack is currently a custom mod pack being developed by TigersFangs. It is subject to change frequently, and some times drastically. I am still tuning, organizing, and feeling out this mod pack. Please be aware that worlds may or may not be transferable between version updates. I do the absolute best that I can to make sure that ID's stay the same forward and backward, but not all mods in the pack today are guaranteed to be there tomorrow.

SAVES WILL BE BROKEN AT SOME POINT! If you want to avoid this, then do not download an update without first going to the website and checking the version change log at the bottom of the page.

If you have any questions, tweet me @TigerzFangz

name: From The Darkness
description:
From The Darkness 1(SSP) and From The Darkness 2(SMP) are two seperate modpacks.  Do not update 1.x to 2.x.

Challenge: Beat the Ender Dragon.
  
Do you like resource management? Do you like adventuring? Do you like having tons of different blocks to create unique buildings? Do you also like dying? How about screaming at Minecraft in a rage then throwing your PC out the window? Are you intrigued by the idea of having a heart attack while playing a video game? If you said yes to 1 or more of these then From The Darkness may be the pack for you! 

--WARNING-- Not for the faint of heart or slight of character, you will die over and over and over again, that is the From The Darkness guarantee!

Disclaimer: Dagarath is making this claim baselessly and in no way actually guarantees anything.  Feel free to stream this, make Let's Plays, Tutorials, etc.  Let me know about them and I will link them on the official website!!

name: Explorer's Modpack
description: Explorer's Modpack is centered around the idea that players are not going to want to stay in one place for a long time. To keep the difficulty up, all armors but Leather and certain other-dimensional armors are also disabled, so players can never get too comfortable or they will get killed, and deal with the effects of the Soft Hardcore mod (limited lives, but renewable with enough gold).

The mods in this pack are well known, so players will not be completely lost. Each mod works well complementing each other mod while giving the game at least a "little bit" of everything that players usually look for. name: DarkActiveTEK
description:
A modpack built around the amazing features of GregTech Mod. We love GregTech machines, power storage/generation, and some of the difficult elements it introduces. Unleashed can feel a bit to easy at times. However, we still feel that GregTech takes things to far, so we will be updating configs and removing specific nerfs and "buffing" certain elements unique to GregTech. 

Furthermore, we added mods that we feel are core or important to any good modded server. Mods like IC2, ThermalExpansion, Buildcraft, Thaumcraft, Forestry, ComputerCraft, etc. From that point we sprinkle on other mods that are fun and bring new elements to the game. However, its important that all these other mods aren't overpowered and make things to easy once again. We do this by mostly editing configuration files and if that doesn't work banning specific items on our servers.

The goal of the modpack is to create a difficult but fun modpack that doesn't have that super gridny feeling. So game balance is quite important overall in this pack.

(PS: If you would like to stream or make videos of this pack, please do! It was built by streamers, for streamers!)

name: KrisCraft
description:
Everything is based around GregTech. All the settings are on hard and the focus of the pack is technology.

Advancing in technology should take time and effort, if you like to become "immortal" and have access to what blocks you want quickly I suggest you go in creative mode or play an easier pack.

This pack tries to delay the endgame phase where you fly around and build whatever you want, but with some time and effort you'll still get there.

The red names represents the mods, blue ones are "addon mods" while green are client side mods. Client mods you can add or remove as you like, the rest of the optional mods can be removed to make the pack a bit more challenging.

Disclaimer: Not all the videos you see when clicking the "Videos" button on the KrisCraft page is not videos I made, videos I am in or videos featuring the modpack.

More info and challenges found here: http://bit.ly/SkyFactory

This pack is meant to be a combination of as many useful mods as possible in order to give the player as many different options as possible. With the addition of the Blood Magic mod in addition to the standard Thaumcraft and Ars Magica, you are now presented with 3 different magic options which each have their own strong suits. Together they combine to make one incredibly powerful mage. In addition we have added many tech mods that make the vision of a completely industrialized Minecraft a possibility. When the magic mods are combined with the tech mods its possible to become the almighty Technomancer whose power is unrivaled in the world of Minecraft. Get ready for a trip into another world with the introduction of...The Gamehendge Pack.

description:
The Private Filming Version of Yogscast Complete

For the same reason, do not distribute this pack to unauthorised users.

Requires Java 7 Update 67 or newer to run. Built for Minecraft 1.6.4 with Forge #965.

name: Yogscast Complete Pack
description:
The greatest hits of the Yogscast in one place, past, present and future!

From as far back as the Jaffa Factory all the way to their present interplanetary adventure and places beyond, join the Yogscast in their modded Minecraft adventures with this all-in-one modpack for every occasion!

Whether you're travelling through space with Galacticraft and the latest technology of Mekanism, discovering the secrets of the arcane with Ars Magica and Thaumcraft, or just building a monument to your own vanity with Statues and Carpenter's Blocks, we have you covered.

Perhaps you like dabbling in Forbidden Magic though? Augmenting your very self with Advanced Genetics? Is an underwater adventure with the mastery of Mariculture what you seek? Maybe you just want to create your own vineyard with GrowthCraft's crops of wonder, or a dwarven ale brewery. You could take advantage of Minechem to end world hunger... or just feed your own addictions.

You've seen where the Yogscast's adventures have taken them before - come find out where they might be heading!

Requires Java 7 Update 67 or newer to run. Built for Minecraft 1.6.4 with Forge #965.

Happy crafting! For support, please visit the support section of http://resonant-rise.com!

name: Beepercraft
description:
Beepercraft revolves around teamwork and the idea of preventing lag and having fun!
Installation Guide:
Click install modpack
Select the mods you want - We use recommended (Click button on bottom) on Beepercraft's server
You are in!  If you get an error you can email Beeperdp@gmail.com - You will get a faster than usual response! If your game crashes on startup Beeperdp automatically gets a report and will try to fix the bug!

Pro Tips:
If your game crashes, the report is automatically sent to Beeperdp to look at! You can email beeperdp@gmail.com for crash help if you need it - You don't need to email the crash just the time of crash!
If you are lagging, look on youtube on how to install optifine!

Press You Numpad 0 key to look at the Waila settings. Waila is what shows what you are looking at!

Pressing L enables/disables global lighting - on servers you may not want to do this without asking everyone

description:
Ultimate Innovation! A blast from the past that showcases changes and improvements that have transpired while mods that started in 1.4 or earlier have developed. Come check out how mods have evolved and innovated since their creation. If you're missing the days of old but still crave what's new, this might be the pack for you.
Follow @malice936 on twitter to find out where this pack is heading in the future
Check out the action and dev versions @ twitch.tv/straymav

Truly this pack is an homage to, and inspired by, the old Ultimate pack. This pack includes the highest quality mods and addons to the classics in order to encourage players to go back and touch older creative methods of automation and progression.

name: Twisted Sin
description:
Are you ready to take a dive into the Twisted Sin world? The Twisted Sin modpack is the next step in modded minecraft survival, bringing us out of the 1.6.4 days and into the 1.7.2/1.7.10! If you are interested in dungeon crawling, difficult mobs, and strange dimensions, this pack is for you! Don't fear, it does contain some tech to help you automate and process your ores.

Want to know more about the pack creator? Head on over to http://twitch.tv/MindlessPuppetz to see him stream or follow him on Twitter: @MindlessPuppetz

Please report errors for 1.7.2 here: https://github.com/MindlessPuppetz/1.7.2_TwistedSin/issues
Please report errors for 1.7.10 here: https://github.com/MindlessPuppetz/1.7.10_TwistedSin/issues

name: Technicality
description:
A cool pack designed for balance and fun. Contains Botania, Thaumcraft 4, Blood Magic and Buildcraft mods (inc Additional Buildcraft, Railcraft and Forestry), Tinkers Construct (plus); with a bunch of other mods to make the experience fun.

List of pack permissions contained here:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10dRgWvgGNVXpFikkO5yIl2afBu8refz2gkeSDikgDqI/edit?usp=sharing

name: RightToRebel
description: This time, there will be more choices, alternative tech mods as well as options for those who'd prefer to avoid tech altogether. Don't like tech? Would rather be a wizard of the dark arts? Redux allows you to experience all the forbidden magics of Blood magic, Ars magica and Thaumcraft and all the wonderful inventions that come with them. Are you a farmer at heart? Then magical crops is here for you! Produce all the materials you want, in the comfort of your fields and crops! For the warrior amongst you we have buffed monsters with better weapons, better attacks and more variety!

name: Shenanigans
description:
The Shenanigans Pack is a multi-dimensional, non-tech, adventure-oriented pack with lots of paths to do everything. While other packs focus on technology such as machines and power, or even on enhancing vanilla minecraft, The Shenanigans Pack focuses on making mods work together to such an extent that the only way to progress while retaining multiple path-trees is to adventure, mine, or build. It is multi-dimensional by having specific mods add specific dimensions which gives the pack a more direct adventure path and more avenues of adventure for player. There is no tech (IC2, BC2, etc.), no vanilla biomes, and no lack of adventure.    

Special Note From The Creator - The shenanigans will mess with your mind!  It's my vision of what minecraft should be with a good mix of basic tech & gravity, adventure, rpg, and various automation aspects with an indirect leveling system.

Modpack Maker (NinetyFour) - http://www.twitter.com/IamNinetyFour

name: Zack's Pack
description:
THE FIRST EVER PUBLIC MODPACK WITH OVER 300 LOADED MODS! ZACKS PACK! The Chuck Norris of Modpacks!  Now that i have your attention, let me explain exactly why this Modpack is the Mother of all Modpacks. The Pack has over "300 loaded mods..", and counting! Mainly focusing on longevity, adventure, and fulfillment. If you're looking for a fun Modpack, that'll last; this is the Modpack for you! 

WARNING: Due to this Modpack's high-mod-count; depending on your computer, you can receive quite a bit of lagg at times; as well as crashes. I do recommend to: backup before, In the middle of, or even after your gameplay.

Welcome to the GamerCraft mod pack! This mod pack is based around giving the player a hardcore adventure and having fun while doing it! When you think of hardcore you almost immediately think hard. But I think of fun, vanilla minecraft is to easy to me and I think it's just lacking content and activities to do which is exactly why I made this mod pack so that the player doesn't get board after there first day playing which I hope i succeeded this goal when you play this pack for the first time. Happy playing! - ReDesignedHD

Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/ReDesignedHD
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/ReDesignedHD

name: L33tPack
description:
The L33t Pack is a private custom mod pack designed for the L33t Network to use. The pack was formed with the idea of a hardcore theme.  This includes slower progression and harder recipes.  Your enemies are the environment, other teams, and hunger.  The goal here is to have a fun, PvP style server where you can work with your team to come up on top.

This pack will be updated often to keep mods to their most up to date releases.

name: Bo buddy bunkers
description:
Welcome to Bo-Buddy Bunkers!
You are in placed into the past, but one that is more futuristic than you would think. 
Because of a lack of a renaissance age, science had more time to advance, and put those in the past far ahead of that in real life. 
Because of such an up rise of advanced technologies, nations began to feud over the technology in one and another hands.

After a ravaging war, you the player are dropped into the war torn remains, and it is up to you to rebuild society as we know it. Build new cities, both above and under the ground with friends, or use specialty weaponry to fight off who wants to take what is rightfully yours.
Using an arsenal of pre-war bunkers, both public and military oriented, you as the player are challenged with using past technologies recovered from the pre-war bunkers and cities and creating new ones to rebuild a once thriving world.

name: Hermitcraft Modsauce
description:
Hermitcraft ModSauce is a beta 1.7.X mod pack to play and learn a variety mods.
Currently it has a bunch of old favorites like Thermal Expansion, MineFactory Reloaded, Extra Utilities, etc...

Some of the new mods are: Beheaded, Electrical Age, InvisibLights, Ping, Soul Shards: Reborn, EnderTech,  and more.

The overworld is your best friend, days last longer nights even shorter and ores galore you'll never get tired exploring and harnessing the bright and dark sides of nature. When prepared step into one of the harder magical dimensions or stay at home with the flowers.....you decide.

Natural Magic is currently still under development, so expect changes in future updates.  This will also include the server creation tool.

Designed By Lewis "WTFGeeks!"

description: This is a high-tech, space-based modpack. Explore the space; Build a moon base; Build big reactors and big missiles; and even a Spaceship factory! This pack will surely bring a galactic experience.

name: Survivalists' Nightmare
description:
If you thought UHS was difficult you're in for a wake up call. Good luck trying to punch trees this time sonny boy. You're going to need to scrounge for sticks and stones if you hope to survive and even then you're going to have a tough time of it.
A unique modpack devoid of all standard amenities such as Inventory tweaks, Optifine, and even NEI.
Designed to be difficult and challenging, where the winters are long, food is scarce, and everything from dirt to stone will fall on your head if you give it the chance.

Feel free to stream, Youtube, Ect.

For beginners I recommend you keep the wiki page open.
 http://wiki.terrafirmacraft.com/

The Ashcraft 1.7.10 modpack is full of deadly dungeons with awesome loot, complicated tech, effective tools, destructive weapons aesthetic builds, mega sorting systems and the ease of automation.

Livestream: twitch.tv/heph YouTube: youtube.com/HephOnYT

description:
Paradise-Reloaded Whitelisted Pack.
